title: Youth unemployment rate in Botswana in 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Youth unemployment rate, containing a total of 21 data points.
Overall Youth unemployment rate has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2000 and 2001.
Maximum Youth unemployment rate, about 46.62 was reported at Year 2003
The lowest Youth unemployment rate, of value 30.77 was reported at Year 2008
